        h2 Downloading Typescript
        p
          | Getting Typescript, if you don't already, is pretty easy. Just run
          code npm install typescript -g
          | or, you're itching for the next release,
          code npm install typescript@latest -g
          | The -g ensures that it is installed globally, but you will most likely want it locally in your projects as well. We'll cover that later.
